<http://www.spektrix.com/gatewaytheatre/event/96801ADHLKNLHKQQPHHDBRLVLVNSHTGBL> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name " Acting for Stage and Film C (Ages 14-18)";
  schema:description """
	Acting for Stage & Film C<span><br/></span>Ages 14-18<span><br/></span>Sept 13, 2026 - Apr 25, 2027<span><br/></span>Sundays, 1:00pm-4:30pm <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>In this class, students will be honing stage/theatre acting technique and ensemble-building throughout the year, with in-depth instruction on acting for film. Students of all levels of experience are welcome to this class, but a strong desire for developing technique is essential.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From September to December, the class will focus on acting technique fundamentals, and students will develop performance presence and confidence. Students will then shift into camera work: refining their skills to focus on film acting, and gaining skills in self-taping and auditioning. Students will each present and take home one (1) taped film monologue in December.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The second half of the year shifts to stage performance, where students will work on a script and expand their skills in physical character work and live storytelling. In April, family and friends will be invited to a presentation of the full play.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The tuition fee includes a longer instruction time (3.5 hours per session), live, on-camera acting instruction, and monologue recordings.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Students of this class will also be given access to attend rehearsals of appropriate Gateway Theatre MainStage productions.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Mandatory class dates:<span><br/></span>Sundays, March 7, April 4, 11, 18 & 25, 2027<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please note: All class withdrawals are subject to a 30% course withdrawal fee. View full <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.gatewaytheatre.com/gateway-academy-terms-conditions\">Refund/Cancellation Policy here</a>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-09-13T13:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
