<http://www.spektrix.com/gatewaytheatre/event/92401AJSJQHTGHCTNCGHBVPSTGHPJLLLT> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "[2026] Musical Theatre Intro 2 Winter (Ages 6-7)";
  schema:description """
	Musical Theatre Intro (Ages 6-7)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Jan 10 – April 25 2026<span><br/></span>Saturdays, 9:15 AM - 10:30 AM<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Maximum 12 students<span><br/></span>Price: $319<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Through each 12-week session, Musical Theatre Intro students will sing, dance, act, and have fun! Students of this class will be introduced to the skills needed to perform in a musical in a joyful and creative environment. At the end of the session, the class will culminate in an interactive Open Studio experience, where family and friends get to participate in the warm-ups and skill-building theatre activities the class does each week. Students will also share a short song, scene, or choreography.
""";
