    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Musical Theatre Intro Fall (Ages 6-7)";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Musical Theatre Intro - Fall</span><span><br/></span>Ages 6-7<span><br/></span>Sept 12, 2026 - Dec 12, 2026<span><br/></span>Saturdays, 10:45am-12:15pm <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Sing, dance, act and have fun! Students of this class will be introduced to the skills needed to perform in a musical in a joyful and creative environment. At the end of each session, the class will culminate in an interactive Open Studio experience, where family and friends get to participate in the warm-ups and skill-building theatre activities. Students will also share a short song, scene, or choreography.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please note: All class withdrawals are subject to a 30% course withdrawal fee. View full <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.gatewaytheatre.com/gateway-academy-terms-conditions\">Refund/Cancellation Policy here</a><span><br/></span>
""";
